data.description: Indulge in the highly sought after Riverfront neighborhood of Greater First Colony. This refurbished classic Cape Code offers timeless charm and contemporary updates. Upon entry you will be greeted by hardwood floors that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas to create an ideal space for entertaining. The heart of the home boast granite countertops, custom cabinetry, nonskid tile, and newer modern appliances; combining style and functionality. Crown molding accentuates the unique architectural details. Four fireplaces strategically placed throughout the home creates an atmosphere of warmth and relaxation. Designed to accommodate multigenerational living with a convenient in-law suite, complete with its own private entrance, offering flexibility for families of all ages. Privacy fenced yard. For a low annual membership fee, you can enjoy year-round resort lifestyle, with beach, marina access, storage, heated pool, pickleball courts and more! HOA optional.
